<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-17231] Upgrade cassandra-driver-core to 3.12.1</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17231</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current Cassandra driver version is 3.11.0, which uses a vulnerable version of jackson-databind.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We may want to switch to the re-branded com.datastax.oss:java-driver-core 4.13.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
