                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17468670" author="jmckenzie" created="Tue, 4 Jan 2022 15:05:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The 4.x driver has (as I understand it second hand) API breaking changes in it that have sweeping consequences for many things written to the 3.x driver.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Perhaps we should first look to an update to the deps in the bundled driver to a non-vulnerable version of the jackson-databind lib.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17470829" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 7 Jan 2022 19:05:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well, 3.11.0 &lt;em&gt;is&lt;/em&gt; the latest non-4.x driver: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/datastax/java-driver/tags&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/datastax/java-driver/tags&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I suspect we need to take the plunge to 4.x, but a very cursory attempt shows indeed it will not be a quick drop-in replacement.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17941578" author="michaelsembwever" created="Mon, 7 Apr 2025 13:11:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Latest 3.x version is now 3.12.1, and it&apos;s an ASF release post-donation of the driver.&lt;br/&gt;
Shall we use this ticket to upgrade to that ?  (Leaving the bigger upgrade work to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20326&quot; title=&quot;Decouple java driver dependency from server code; Upgrade to 4.x driver for tests and tools&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-20326&quot;&gt;CASSANDRA-20326&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;patch: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/compare/cassandra-5.0...thelastpickle:cassandra:mck/17231/5.0&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/compare/cassandra-5.0...thelastpickle:cassandra:mck/17231/5.0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
ci, pre-commit w/ upgrades:   &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13075843/13075843_ci_summary_thelastpickle_mck-17231-5.0_204.html.download.zip&quot; title=&quot;ci_summary_thelastpickle_mck-17231-5.0_204.html.download.zip attached to CASSANDRA-17231&quot;&gt;ci_summary_thelastpickle_mck-17231-5.0_204.html.download.zip&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; and &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13075844/13075844_results_details_thelastpickle_mck-17231-5.0_204.tar.xz&quot; title=&quot;results_details_thelastpickle_mck-17231-5.0_204.tar.xz attached to CASSANDRA-17231&quot;&gt;results_details_thelastpickle_mck-17231-5.0_204.tar.xz&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17941579" author="brandon.williams" created="Mon, 7 Apr 2025 13:13:14 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shall we use this ticket to upgrade to that ?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+1, let&apos;s do that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17941610" author="michaelsembwever" created="Mon, 7 Apr 2025 14:18:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/694a88bdbe9aa6a4773c99814da33e0a65030ab3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/694a88bdbe9aa6a4773c99814da33e0a65030ab3&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

